<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>L'Assistant Inclusion</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700;800&family=Source+Sans+3:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root {
      --bg: #0D1B2A; --bg2: #132236; --bg3: #1A2E45; --surface: #1F3650;
      --border: #2A4A68; --accent: #F0A500; --accent2: #3EC9A7;
      --text: #EDF2F7; --muted: #8BA5BF; --danger: #E05C5C;
      --radius: 12px; --radius-lg: 20px;
    }
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif; background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); min-height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
    body::before { content: ''; position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 0; background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 80% 10%, rgba(240,165,0,.07) 0%, transparent 60%), radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 50% at 10% 80%, rgba(62,201,167,.06) 0%, transparent 60%); pointer-events: none; }
    header { position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100; background: rgba(13,27,42,.92); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 0 32px; height: 68px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
    .logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
    .logo-mark { width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 12px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), #e08c00); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 20px; box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(240,165,0,.3); }
    .logo-name { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); }
    .logo-name span { color: var(--accent); }
    .header-langs { display: flex; gap: 6px; }
    .lang-chip { font-size: .72rem; font-weight: 600; padding: 3px 9px; border-radius: 20px; background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--muted); }
    .hero { position: relative; z-index: 1; text-align: center; padding: 52px 24px 36px; }
    .hero-eyebrow { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px; font-size: .78rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .hero-eyebrow::before, .hero-eyebrow::after { content: ''; display: block; width: 28px; height: 1px; background: var(--accent); opacity: .5; }
    .hero h1 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .hero h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent); }
    .hero p { max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto 28px; font-size: 1.02rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.7; font-weight: 300; }
    .tabs-wrapper { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px 60px; width: 100%; }

    /* === ONGLETS === */
    .tabs-nav { display: flex; gap: 4px; margin-bottom: 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); overflow-x: auto; }
    .tab-btn {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px;
      padding: 11px 16px; border: none; background: transparent;
      font-family: 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif; font-size: .88rem; font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--muted); cursor: pointer;
      border-bottom: 2px solid transparent; margin-bottom: -1px;
      white-space: nowrap; transition: color .15s, border-color .15s;
    }
    .tab-btn:hover { color: var(--text); }
    .tab-btn.active { color: var(--accent); border-bottom-color: var(--accent); }
    .tab-panel { display: none; animation: fadeIn .22s ease; }
    .tab-panel.active { display: block; }
    @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(6px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: none; } }
    .coming-soon { text-align: center; padding: 60px 20px; color: var(--muted); }
    .coming-soon .icon { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 12px; }

    footer { position: relative; z-index: 1; text-align: center; padding: 24px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: .78rem; color: var(--muted); }
    footer a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <div class="logo">
      <div class="logo-mark">🌍</div>
      <span class="logo-name">L'Assistant <span>Inclusion</span></span>
    </div>
    <div class="header-langs">
      <span class="lang-chip">FR</span><span class="lang-chip">AR</span><span class="lang-chip">EN</span>
      <span class="lang-chip">ES</span><span class="lang-chip">PT</span><span class="lang-chip">TR</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">Intelligence Artificielle · Accès aux droits</div>
    <h1>Comprendre vos documents<br><em>dans votre langue</em></h1>
    <p>Simplification, traduction et explication des documents administratifs français — accessible à tous.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="tabs-wrapper">
    <!-- NAVIGATION ONGLETS -->
    <nav class="tabs-nav">
      <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="switchTab('simplifier',this)">✂️ Simplifier</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('traduire',this)">🌐 Traduire</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('expliquer',this)">📄 Expliquer un document</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('glossaire',this)">📚 Glossaire</button>
    </nav>

    <!-- PANNEAUX -->
    <div id="tab-simplifier" class="tab-panel active">
      <div class="coming-soon"><div class="icon">✂️</div><p>Onglet <strong>Simplifier</strong> — contenu à venir.</p></div>
    </div>
    <div id="tab-traduire" class="tab-panel">
      <div class="coming-soon"><div class="icon">🌐</div><p>Onglet <strong>Traduire</strong> — contenu à venir.</p></div>
    </div>
    <div id="tab-expliquer" class="tab-panel">
      <div class="coming-soon"><div class="icon">📄</div><p>Onglet <strong>Expliquer</strong> — contenu à venir.</p></div>
    </div>
    <div id="tab-glossaire" class="tab-panel">
      <div class="coming-soon"><div class="icon">📚</div><p>Onglet <strong>Glossaire</strong> — contenu à venir.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer>
    L'Assistant Inclusion · Propulsé par <a href="https://anthropic.com" target="_blank">Claude (Anthropic)</a> · Master Machine Learning · Sorbonne
  </footer>

  <script>
    function switchTab(name, btn) {
      document.querySelectorAll('.tab-panel').forEach(p => p.classList.remove('active'));
      document.querySelectorAll('.tab-btn').forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active'));
      document.getElementById('tab-' + name).classList.add('active');
      btn.classList.add('active');
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
